commands.description:
0 !LPUB SUBMODEL_DISPLAY STUD_STYLE ( PLAIN | THIN_LINE_LOGO | OUTLINE_TOP_LOGO | SHARP_TOP_LOGO | ROUNDED_TOP_LOGO | FLATTENED_TOP_LOGO | HIGH_CONTRAST_PLAIN | HIGH_CONTRAST_THIN_LINE | <stud style integer 0-7> )
- The <stud style integer 0-7> meta value captures the 7 stud style types.
  0 Plain 
  1 Thin line logo 
  2 Outline top logo 
  3 Sharp top logo 
  4 Rounded top logo 
  5 Flattened top logo 
  6 High contrast plain 
  7 High contrast thin line logo
